<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ث ر د:</span> <span class="c2">(ثَرَدَ)</span> الْخُبْزَ كَسَرَهُ مِنْ بَابِ نَصَرَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(ثَرِيدٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(مَثْرُودٌ)</span> وَالِاسْمُ <span class="c2">(الثُّرْدَةُ)</span> بِوَزْنِ الْبُرْدَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>